<br>
I strip you of all afiliation with the Violent Harvest, I hereby declare you anathema!<br>
<br>
The path of hate is best discovered alone.  The path of hate is not learned or observed.  The hate in this one runs very strong.  Let her discover hate and her true power alone.<br>
<br>
The ceremonies concluded. Kassy gone from Neriak.  Creapiing sends a few messages out by dark messengers.  A few *situations* might help the one who knew nothing learn hate.  Creapiiing nodded  in satisfaction.  There was always hope Kassy would learn something...hate...and power... <p>Creapiing V'Etch<BR>
